title: #120: Honey Badger Don't Care
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another fun addition of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys welcome Randall the Honey Badger Guy to discuss his take on a wide range of conspiracy topics including hiss feeling on the Maverick John McCain! Thank you so much for all of your support and hope to see you at one of our upcoming live events.
Sept 5th- The Comedy Store at 8pm
Sept 14th and 15th- The Corner Comedy in Niagara Falls Canada
Oct 12th: The Punchline Philly
Oct 14th: The Syracuse Funny Bone
Nov 3rd: The Secret Group in Houston
Nov 4th: Stateside Theatre in Austin Texas
